content: List 10 animal names where each name begins with a different letter of the alphabet.

Sure, here are ten animal names, each starting with a different letter of the alphabet:

1. Ant
2. Bear
3. Cat
4. Dog
5. Elephant
6. Frog
7. Giraffe
8. Hawk
9. Iguana
10. Jaguar

I hope this helps! If you have any more questions, feel free to ask.
